K12D0844_H0808:422a-30: ji ltar bsgo ba gzhan gyis 'dzin /
K12D0844_H0808:422a-31: rang dang sangs rgyas rnams kyis gsungs /
K12D0844_H0808:422b-0: mthun pa'i tshul gyis mi 'dor la /snyan dang mi snyan @422b ci brjod rnams /
K12D0844_H0808:422b-1: tshangs pa yi dbyangs bzhin du 'ong /
K12D0844_H0808:422b-2: grags thos tsam gyis dbang du byed /
K12D0844_H0808:422b-3: tshul mdzes 'jug pa dag gi brda /
K12D0844_H0808:422b-4: gang la brtsam pa de 'grub cing /
K12D0844_H0808:422b-5: ma zhum mi spor mi 'dor bas /
K12D0844_H0808:422b-6: dbang dang ldan zhing mi g-yo la /gsang ba'i mthu stobs rab tu thob /
K12D0844_H0808:422b-7: yid kyi yul du brda 'byung ba'i /
K12D0844_H0808:422b-8: snga phyi de ma thag pa 'o /
K12D0844_H0808:422b-9: bag chags ma yin rmi lam ni /rgyal po mkhan po slob dpon dang /
K12D0844_H0808:422b-10: che btsan rigs ldan rgyan bcas ldan /
K12D0844_H0808:422b-12: skyes ba bud med bus pa sogs /
K12D0844_H0808:422b-13: rang gi gnas su lhags pa ni /
K12D0844_H0808:422b-14: nye bar 'grub pa'i rtags yin no /
K12D0844_H0808:422b-16: bka' bsgo las byed nyan pa rtags /
K12D0844_H0808:422b-17: ring ba'i gnas nas glu len cing /
K12D0844_H0808:422b-18: rgyang mig lta ba g-yel ba'i rtags /
K12D0844_H0808:422b-19: rang la chad pa'i las rtsom zhing /
K12D0844_H0808:422b-20: nyes lan 'ded pa bzlog pa'i rtags /
K12D0844_H0808:422b-21: zas skom 'dod cing 'khrig lan bsnyag /rang nyid gnod 'gyod ma skongs rtags /
K12D0844_H0808:422b-23: ma dag lus snang nyams pa'i rtags /
K12D0844_H0808:422b-24: rang gi bsgro ba mi nyan zhing /
K12D0844_H0808:422b-26: gnyen pos dbang du ma gyur rtags /
K12D0844_H0808:422b-27: mtshon cha brdung zhing tshad ma ldan /
K12D0844_H0808:422b-28: nus med bya ba mi 'grub pas /
K12D0844_H0808:423a-2: gzhan 'dod rang la med pa dang /
K12D0844_H0808:423a-3: rang gi yod pa 'dod med rnams /
K12D0844_H0808:423a-4: mchod bskang mthun rdzas ma chang rtags /
K12D0844_H0808:423a-5: sha rus khrag sogs longs spyod cing /
K12D0844_H0808:423a-6: ngo mthon rab tu che ba na /
K12D0844_H0808:423a-7: las byas 'grub pa'i rtags yin no /
K12D0844_H0808:423a-8: pha rol dmag tshogs ma byung zhing /
K12D0844_H0808:423a-9: sgo med khang par bdag zhugs la /
K12D0844_H0808:423a-10: ngan sngags gzhan gyis bzlog ba'i rtags /
K12D0844_H0808:423a-11: bye brag sde brgyad so so ni /
K12D0844_H0808:423a-13: pho tshogs nag po bdud kyi rtags /
K12D0844_H0808:423a-14: mo tshogs rgyan bzang ma mo ste /
K12D0844_H0808:423a-15: che btsan 'bag seng gtsug lag khang /
K12D0844_H0808:423a-16: bus pa spra spre rgyal po'i rtags /
K12D0844_H0808:423a-17: mi rta khra spyang ri dvags ni /
K12D0844_H0808:423a-18: brag btsan ri btsan rtags yin no /
K12D0844_H0808:423a-19: chu gnas dud 'gro klu yi rtags /
K12D0844_H0808:423a-20: ma he ra lug mig mang dang /
K12D0844_H0808:423a-21: mun pa bu yug gza' yi rtags /
K12D0844_H0808:423a-22: skyes pa chas bzang 'byor pa can /
K12D0844_H0808:423a-23: ri mtsho la gnas gnod sbyin rtags /
K12D0844_H0808:423a-24: nya pa shan ba bya pa dang /
K12D0844_H0808:423a-25: dmag gi go mtshon srin po'i rtags /
K12D0844_H0808:423a-26: 'di dag sngar bshad bzang ngan sbyar /
K12D0844_H0808:423a-27: bye brag sgrub pa'i rtags su 'gyur /
K12D0844_H0808:423a-29: 'jig rten gyi sde dpon chen po sgrub pa'i rtags kyi le'u ste /
K12D0844_H0808:423a-30: dgu pa'o //de nas gzhan yang rab bshad pa /
K12D0844_H0808:423a-31: dregs pa can gyi khyad par rdzas /
K12D0844_H0808:423b-0: mdzes pa'i gzugs brnyan @423b sku yi rten /
K12D0844_H0808:423b-1: ming nas 'bod pa gsung gi rten /
K12D0844_H0808:423b-2: phyag mtshan dam pa thugs kyi rten /
K12D0844_H0808:423b-3: lug g-yag dkar po sbal sbrul nya /
K12D0844_H0808:423b-4: glang rta sngon po rin po che /
K12D0844_H0808:423b-5: g-yul bshams myur bsgral bya gcan dang /
K12D0844_H0808:423b-6: nal bu shel nag bya nag dang /
K12D0844_H0808:423b-7: rta lug khyi dang rgod nag dang /
K12D0844_H0808:423b-8: ra phag bya khyi dkar po dang /
K12D0844_H0808:423b-9: kla klor rog dom khyi nag /
K12D0844_H0808:423b-10: sbrul nag bya rgod ra skyes dang /
K12D0844_H0808:423b-11: rta ra bya khyi dmar po yi /
K12D0844_H0808:423b-12: snying khrag mgo dang rgyal mtshan ni /
K12D0844_H0808:423b-13: lha klu gnod sbyin srin po dang /
K12D0844_H0808:423b-14: ma mo bdud dang rgyal po ging /
K12D0844_H0808:423b-15: gshin rje gza' dang btsan rnams kyi /
K12D0844_H0808:423b-16: rim bzhin so so brten pa'i rdzas /
K12D0844_H0808:423b-17: rab tu gsang ba nyid yin no /
K12D0844_H0808:423b-18: ae ldan gdug bcas rgyud med kyi /
K12D0844_H0808:423b-19: thod pa mtshon cha phur pa dag /dug khrag rin chen drag po'i 'bru /
K12D0844_H0808:423b-20: kun tshogs rab tu gsang ba'i rdzas /
K12D0844_H0808:423b-21: klu gzung snod ni sha khrag bcas /
K12D0844_H0808:423b-22: ru bzang rigs med myur song chu /
K12D0844_H0808:423b-23: myu gu sna tshogs dri ldan rdzas /
K12D0844_H0808:423b-24: chu drag dpa' rabs dud pa'i rdzas yin no /
K12D0844_H0808:423b-25: mchod rten ri rab rgya gram bcas /
K12D0844_H0808:423b-26: dme rdzas rigs ngan mgo bo gsum /
K12D0844_H0808:423b-28: slar la bzlog pa'i rdzas yin no /
K12D0844_H0808:423b-29: nad gdug bam ril mgo rkang rnam /
K12D0844_H0808:423b-30: rab tu mnan pa'i rdzas yin no /
K12D0844_H0808:423b-31: dug khrag tshogs dang mtshan ma ngan /
K12D0844_H0808:423b-32: dmigs pa'i rten la 'phang ba'i rdzas /
K12D0844_H0808:424a-1: pa'i sa yi rten khang dang /
K12D0844_H0808:424a-2: gdug cing rab tu tsha ba'i shing /
K12D0844_H0808:424a-3: 'bru nag dug khrag bsres pa'i rdzas /
K12D0844_H0808:424a-4: gzhan yang dbang can dregs pa'i 'khor /
K12D0844_H0808:424a-5: so so'i rigs dang sder bcas pa'i /
K12D0844_H0808:424a-6: mthun dang mi mthun gtsang dang sme /bsngags pa'i kun rdzas shes par 'gyur /
K12D0844_H0808:424a-8: rang gi rig 'dzin byang chub sems /
K12D0844_H0808:424a-9: brtul zhugs can gyis 'grub pa yis /
K12D0844_H0808:424a-10: dbus dang mtha' 'kho ba yul rnams dang /
K12D0844_H0808:424a-11: sangs rgyas zhing gi 'jig rten khams /
K12D0844_H0808:424a-12: kun nas sde dpon g-yog bcas pa'i /
K12D0844_H0808:424a-13: yid dang dngos po'i lus can rnams /
K12D0844_H0808:424a-14: khams dang rigs pa bsam pa dang /
K12D0844_H0808:424a-15: skyed pa rten gnas yo byad dang /
K12D0844_H0808:424a-16: ma lus rdzogs par rab tu rtogs /
K12D0844_H0808:424a-17: shes ldan mig can rnams la ston /
K12D0844_H0808:424a-18: de tshe dregs pa'i gtso chen rnams /
K12D0844_H0808:424a-19: da lta nga yis gdams pa yin /
K12D0844_H0808:424a-20: yang dag don la ma 'da' zhig /khyed rnams kyang ni dus nam zhig /
K12D0844_H0808:424a-21: las kyi gnas ngan len spangs te /
K12D0844_H0808:424a-22: byang chub sa la myur 'gro yi /
K12D0844_H0808:424a-23: de bas bka' yi dam mnos la /
K12D0844_H0808:424a-24: ji ltar dmigs pa bzhin bsgrubs shing /
K12D0844_H0808:424a-25: gsang chen nga yi bstan pa'i tshul /
K12D0844_H0808:424a-26: phyi rol phyogs la sogs pa yis /
K12D0844_H0808:424b-0: nyams shing smras par @424b mi 'gyur bas /
K12D0844_H0808:424b-1: rgyas shing bstan par khyod kyis byos /
K12D0844_H0808:424b-3: 'jig rten gyi sde dpon chen po'i rten rdzas dang /
K12D0844_H0808:424b-4: las kyi gnyer bsgo ba'i le'u ste bcu pa'o //de
K12D0844_H0808:424b-5: nas bcom ldan 'das de bzhin gshegs ba thams cad
K12D0844_H0808:424b-6: kyi sku dang gsung dang thugs kyi bdag nyid gsang
K12D0844_H0808:424b-7: ba chen po'i sku'i rnam par rol pa chen po
K12D0844_H0808:424b-8: de dag nyid kyi sku la rab tu bsdus pa
K12D0844_H0808:424b-9: mdzad de dgyes pa'i gsung gis 'di skad ces bka'
K12D0844_H0808:424b-10: stsal to / kye ma 'dus pa'i 'khor tshogs rnams /
K12D0844_H0808:424b-11: bdud dang gshin rje la sogs pa'i /
K12D0844_H0808:424b-12: 'jig rten dbang chen gtso chen rnams /
K12D0844_H0808:424b-13: mthar thug mya ngan 'das nas kyang /
K12D0844_H0808:424b-14: dus gsum sangs rgyas thams cad kyi /
K12D0844_H0808:424b-15: bstan pa'i tha tshig sgrub pa dang /
K12D0844_H0808:424b-16: rnal 'byor lam gyi grogs mdzad phyir /
K12D0844_H0808:424b-17: drag po'i sku gsung thugs nyid dang /
K12D0844_H0808:424b-18: yon tan 'phrin las sna tshogs ston /
K12D0844_H0808:424b-19: phyi ma'i dus na rig pa 'dzin /
K12D0844_H0808:424b-20: skyes bu brtson ldan rnams kyis ni /
K12D0844_H0808:424b-21: gnyis su 'dzin par yongs mi bya /
K12D0844_H0808:424b-22: yul snang phyi nang ma lus kun /
K12D0844_H0808:424b-23: rang rigs sems kyi rgyal por bsgrub /
K12D0844_H0808:424b-24: de ni ma bcos yul mi bral /
K12D0844_H0808:424b-25: ma chad ma lhung bdag po med /gnyis med mnyam nyid lhun gyis grub /
K12D0844_H0808:424b-26: nges 'gyur sbar blang rtsol sems bral /ma lus rtsa
K12D0844_H0808:424b-27: ba snying gi srog /de nyid shes bya rab tu
K12D0844_H0808:425a-2: gal te nga dang dregs pa can /
K12D0844_H0808:425a-3: so so rang rgyud ldan pa yis /
K12D0844_H0808:425a-4: gnyis 'dzin yid kyis rtog spyod cing /
K12D0844_H0808:425a-5: mtshan mar rab tu sgom byed par /
K12D0844_H0808:425a-6: rkang med khams gsum bgrod 'dod cing /
K12D0844_H0808:425a-7: mig med stong gsum blta dang mtshungs /
K12D0844_H0808:425a-8: bdud bzhi dga' ba skyed par byed /
K12D0844_H0808:425a-9: de bas rigs mchog ma rnams kyis /
K12D0844_H0808:425a-10: gsang bdag nga nyid shes par gyis /
K12D0844_H0808:425a-11: zhes bka' stsal nas nyid kyi sku gsung thugs kyi
K12D0844_H0808:425a-12: dkyil 'khor chen po chos nyid de bzhin nyid spros
K12D0844_H0808:425a-13: dang bral ba'i dbyings su thim par mdzad do /
K12D0844_H0808:425a-14: 'jig rten gyi sde dpon chen po 'khor dang bcas
K12D0844_H0808:425a-15: pa chos sku mthar thug tu sgrub par gdams pa'i
K12D0844_H0808:425a-16: le'u ste bcu gcig pa'o //dregs pa can gyi sde
K12D0844_H0808:425a-17: dpon 'jig rten mchod bstod sgrub pa rtsa ba'i rgyud
